# ğŸ“š Personal Study Planner

A simple Streamlit app that generates a **day-wise study plan** based on your exam date, subjects and daily available study hours.

## ğŸš€ Features

- Select exam date
- Enter subjects (one per line)
- Choose how many hours you can study each day
- Automatically calculates:
  - Days left until exam
  - Recommended total hours per subject
  - Day-wise schedule (main subject + hours)
- Download the generated plan as a CSV file

## ğŸ›  Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- datetime module

